{"tid":896584,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同事約我睇戲，唔知點推好","createTime":"2018-11-10T07:17:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T08:09:15.000Z","uid":32938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"486a7acfc25bb96bda90bc49249788509eacd1b5","tid":896584,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:17:51.000Z","msg":"又唔係好熟，大半年只係一齊食過三幾次晏。Lunch time食下飯吹下水冇乜所謂，但我總係覺得一男一女去睇戲有啲怪，唔知點推好。唔推佢怕佢諗多左，推佢又怕佢以為我諗多左&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"7bde448cf4a6d9693759db15085edf2bc710701f","tid":896584,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:19:38.000Z","msg":"起完底原來又係波台狗"},{"pid":"529fa0c38a24a8212e6bcfc7cf3af94e8d88a7fb","tid":896584,"uid":2393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37253d12d4c01345d1d1b5f287863380f3d432d","tid":896584,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"直接推啦，男人老狗扭扭擰擰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}